transcripts.text: Come on, let's sing together.  Where two or more are gathered in His name He is there.  All for all who come, who run to Him in faith.  He is there.  Come on, sing it to Him.  There is power in the name of Jesus.  There is power, power in His name.  There is power.  No No He is here.  Do you believe it tonight?  Oh, the world has come to silence every doubt.  He is here.  There is power in the name of Jesus.  There is power, power in his name.  There is power in His name.  There is power, power in His name.  Whoa!  One name, one name can save.  One name makes every change.  One name always.  One name Jesus.  One name, one name remains.  One name we will proclaim.  One name always.  One name there is power.  Sing it.  In the name of Jesus, there is power.  There is power in the name of Jesus.  There is power in the name of Jesus.  There is power in the name of Jesus.  There is power in the name of Jesus.  There is power, power in his name.  There's power in his name.  There's power in his name.
